Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠! 你最近去哪了?\N{\rENG}Pearl! Where've you been? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}...找橄榄石啊\N{\rENG}Looking for Peridot. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也就几这几天\N{\rENG}For a few days straight. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我知道我也许...\N{\rENG}Steven, I know I might have...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让你们 失望了\N{\rENG}Disappointed all of you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道石榴还在生我的气 \N{\rENG}I know Garnet's very upset with me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我要向她证明她可以再次信任我\N{\rENG}But I'm going to prove to her that she can trust me again. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.88,0:00:23.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 石榴! 我刚刚在寻找橄榄石哦!\N{\rENG}Oh, Garnet! I was just looking for Peridot! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她肯定在什么地方 对吧?\N{\rENG}She's bound to be somewhere, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.88,0:00:26.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有什么新想法吗?\N{\rENG}Any new ideas? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我对不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.94,0:00:37.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁想参加公路自驾游?!\N{\rENG}Who wants to go on a road trip?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...我来的不是时候?\N{\rENG}Um...Is this a bad time? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.14,0:00:42.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 请继续\N{\rENG}No. Please continue. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 我要开车去隔壁州-拱顶石\N{\rENG}Well, I gotta drive over to the next state, keystone. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.43,0:00:46.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你指 拱顶石州?\N{\rENG}You mean, the keystone state? 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 那个州就叫"拱顶石"\N{\rENG}Right, the state named keystone. 
Dialogue: 600,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.48,Hint,,0,0,0,,"拱顶石州"对应现实中的宾夕法尼亚州. 格雷格手中册子上的轮廓与宾夕法尼亚州相近 \N且宾夕法尼亚处于最初的13个殖民地中央 曾被称为"The Keystone State". 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在网上的留言板认识了一个人\N{\rENG}I met a guy on an Internet message board
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.66,0:00:53.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}卖的洗车用的刷子简直白菜价!\N{\rENG}who's selling car-wash brushes for real cheap! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只需要到拱顶石州跟他碰头并拿货就好\N{\rENG}I just gotta meet him in keystone and pick 'em up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不喜欢那种刷子 用来洗毛发时总感觉怪怪的\N{\rENG}I don't like those brushes. They feel weird on your fur. 
Dialogue: 600,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.16,Hint,,0,0,0,,详见第一季第6集 Cat Fingers
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 你喜欢汽车旅馆吗?\N{\rENG}Well, do you like motels? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很可能哦!\N{\rENG}Probably! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你愿意在汽车旅馆里\N{\rENG}Think you'd like to stay at a motel
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}陪你最喜欢的老爸吗?\N{\rENG}with your favorite dad? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不觉得你是我的最爱哦...\N{\rENG}I don't know if you're my favorite...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?\N{\rENG}What? Huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.78,0:01:12.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 你个崽子 给我过来\N{\rENG}Oh, you kidder. Come here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.06,0:01:14.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我等不及享受客房服务了!\N{\rENG}I can't wait to get room service! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想的是"饭店"\N{\rENG}You're thinking of a hotel. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们要去的是"汽车旅馆"\N{\rENG}We're going to a motel! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那里有泳池和免费冰块\N{\rENG}It'll have a pool and free ice. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.33,0:01:25.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且它就在全世界最好的餐厅旁边!\N{\rENG}And it's right next to the best diner in the world! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也要去\N{\rENG}I'm coming, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.80,0:01:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}更好了!\N{\rENG}Even better! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 石榴 我知道我有点过度渲染了\N{\rENG}Hey, Garnet, I know I'm talking this place up, 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实没听上去那么好\N{\rENG}but it ain't exactly the ritz. 
Dialogue: 600,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.38,Hint,,0,0,0,,"the ritz"可能指的是伦敦的五星级酒店The Ritz hotel( 利兹酒店) 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我自己会做判断的\N{\rENG}I'll be the judge of that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 这样的话...公路旅行!\N{\rENG}Well, in that case...Road trip! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}公路旅行!\N{\rENG}Road trip! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}公路旅行\N{\rENG}Road trip. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好极了!\N{\rENG}Wonderful! 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会确保紫晶知道要...\N{\rENG}I'll make sure Amethyst knows that...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...再见\N{\rENG}Well, goodbye. 
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.93,0:01:50.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这会很有趣 对吧 老爸?\N{\rENG}This is gonna be fun, right, dad? 
Dialogue: 600,0:01:59.33,0:02:02.30,Hint,,0,0,0,,现实中也有一家"Keystone Motel"坐落于St. Pete Beach Florida.\N那家汽车旅馆曾被宇宙小子的粉丝们恶搞过--有人在Google Plus上\N留下差评 称"马桶被冻住了""披萨是方形的""游泳池被完全蒸发"之类的. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}另一个汽车旅馆的优势-\N{\rENG}Another great thing about motels--
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能直接开到客房门前!\N{\rENG}you can drive right up to your door! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要在泳池里畅游 点播一部大片 享受免费冰块!\N{\rENG}I'm gonna swim in the pool, order a movie, get free ice! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次一定会超赞的!\N{\rENG}It's gonna be great! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}之前先让我检查一下有没有床虱啊!\N{\rENG}Not before we check for bedbugs, it isn't! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Mm. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好消息! 没有床虱!\N{\rENG}Good news! We're bugless! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 有消息了\N{\rENG}Oop, that's my cue. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你不介意在我回来前"守住城堡"吗?\N{\rENG}Hey, do you mind holding down the fort till I get back? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好 那我去和卖隧道刷的人碰面了\N{\rENG}Great. I'm off to see a man about a tunnel brush. 
Dialogue: 600,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.04,Hint,,0,0,0,,格雷格此处的话是"see a man about a dog/ horse"的变种.\N原话从对比赛下注的委婉表达 演变成为避免流露真实原因 用来结束对话的用语
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个网友\N{\rENG}An Internet man. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果一小时内我没回来 记得报警\N{\rENG}If I'm not back in an hour, call the police. 
Dialogue: 600,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.20,Hint,,0,0,0,,格雷格此处的话是"If I'm not back [ soon] call the police"的变种\N这里应该是致敬默片时代的Keystone Kops
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好～的!\N{\rENG}Oh-kay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.84,0:02:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}跟我一起蹦吧 石榴!\N{\rENG}Bounce with me, Garnet! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或-或者我们也可以看看宣传册子\N{\rENG}O-or we could look at brochures. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢～拱顶石洞穴\N{\rENG}Ooh, keystone caverns. 
Dialogue: 600,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.46,Hint,,0,0,0,,"Keystone Caverns"可能指的是"Crystal Cave";"Crystal Cave"是宾夕法尼亚州东南部的一处自然景观. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HE79069&}要冷静\N{\rENG}{\c&HE79069&}Calm down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H5E37D3&}我不想原谅珍珠!\N{\rENG}{\c&H5E37D3&}I don't feel like forgiving Pearl! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HE79069&}我不理解\N{\rENG}{\c&HE79069&}Don't understand
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HE79069&}我们必须要!\N{\rENG}{\c&HE79069&}we must! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H5E37D3&}如果你不想听 你可以离开啊!\N{\rENG}{\c&H5E37D3&}If you're not going to listen, then you can just go! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们必须放下这件事 红宝石\N{\rENG}We must move past this, Ruby. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她向我们撒谎 好让我们组成红玛瑙!\N{\rENG}She lied to us so we'd form sardonyx! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她骗了我们! 你不觉得被利用了吗?\N{\rENG}She tricked us! Don't you feel used?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石! 蓝宝石! 我-\N{\rENG}Ruby! Sapphire! I--
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你选择将这件事过度抬高\N{\rENG}you're choosing to take it personally. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是融合 蓝宝石!\N{\rENG}It's fusion, Sapphire! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有什么对于我们 相比融合 更重要?!\N{\rENG}What's more personal to us than fusion?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道你仍然很生气\N{\rENG}I know you're still upset. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 所以只是我喽?\N{\rENG}Oh, so it's just me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然不是\N{\rENG}Of course not. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你难道看不出我完全被愤怒吞没了?\N{\rENG}Can't you see I'm completely engulfed with rage? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 我怎么感觉不到 ?!\N{\rENG}Well, it doesn't feel like it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们越早原谅珍珠 \N{\rENG}The sooner we forgive Pearl, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对我们所有人都越好\N{\rENG}the better it will be for us all. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.62,0:03:35.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你 并非 层次更高 像 你 自以为 那样!\N{\rENG}You're not as above this as you think you are! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 我就是\N{\rENG}Yes, I am. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不可能永远生她的气\N{\rENG}You can't stay angry with her forever. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.96,0:03:46.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想赌赌吗?\N{\rENG}Wanna bet? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石 注意地毯 \N{\rENG}Ruby, the carpet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-我都不能-啊!\N{\rENG}You--I can't even--ugh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很高兴 再次见到你?\N{\rENG}Nice to see you again? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很高兴见到你\N{\rENG}Nice to see you, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 红宝石\N{\rENG}Hey, Ruby. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.96,0:04:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想在泳池里游泳吗?\N{\rENG}You wanna swim in the pool? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可是融合 史蒂文!\N{\rENG}It's fusion, Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}感觉蓝宝石根本就不在乎!\N{\rENG}It's like Sapphire doesn't even care! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"而且我们应该用'成年人'的视角看问题"\N{\rENG}And we're supposed to be the bigger gem about this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们 一 直 是 "成年人"!\N{\rENG}We're always the bigger gem! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 不行! 这次不行! 这件事! 不行!\N{\rENG}Well, not this time! Not about this! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧 为什么不在泳池里先冷静一下呢?\N{\rENG}Come on, why don't you come cool down in the pool? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 才不需要冷-静呢!\N{\rENG}I don't need to cool down! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快啊 红宝石 水很爽～哦!\N{\rENG}Come on, Ruby. The water's nice! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么她 总是 表现的像 我才是 荒谬的一方?\N{\rENG}Why does she always act like I'm being ridiculous? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就只因为她想伪装成\N{\rENG}Just because she wants to pretend
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}自己没有感情一样\N{\rENG}that she doesn't have feelings?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石?\N{\rENG}Ruby? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你把泳池变成温泉了!\N{\rENG}You made a warm spot! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 是"烫泉"了!\N{\rENG}Ah! A hot spot! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}水开了!\N{\rENG}Boiling! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我还是回屋吧\N{\rENG}Uh, I'm gonna go back to the room. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蓝宝石?\N{\rENG}Sapphire? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你好 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Hello, Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你...还-还-还好吗?\N{\rENG}A-are you...D-d-doin'okay? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-很-好\N{\rENG}I'm fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好-吧\N{\rENG}O-okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想-想一起看电视吗?\N{\rENG}W-wanna watch TV together? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.32,0:05:04.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可以\N{\rENG}Sure. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈 频道的号码都乱了\N{\rENG}Huh. The channels are all the wrong numbers. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿～你能用你的预知能力\N{\rENG}Hey, can you use your future powers
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}预测一下我最喜欢的频道吗?\N{\rENG}to predict what channel I'd love the most? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...43 但也没什么\N{\rENG}Hmm...43. But there's not much on. 
Dialogue: 600,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.42,Hint,,0,0,0,,宾夕法尼亚州的43频道为标清Nickelodeon( 尼克) 台\NNickelodeon为Cartoon Network( 卡通网络 "宇宙小子"的东家) 的竞争对手
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 蓝宝石...\N{\rENG}Hey, Sapphire...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}即使我这样做 红宝石也不会听的\N{\rENG}Even if I do, Ruby won't listen. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?\N{\rENG}Huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你会说我该和红宝石谈谈\N{\rENG}You're going to say I should talk to Ruby, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这没用\N{\rENG}but it won't help. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但-但她看起来非常生气\N{\rENG}B-but she seems really upset. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这无关紧要\N{\rENG}That doesn't matter. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她不可能永远生珍珠的气 \N{\rENG}We can't stay mad at Pearl forever, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且她也不可能永远生我的气 \N{\rENG}and she can't stay mad at me forever. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且之后她会回心转意并发现我是对的\N{\rENG}And then she'll come back and see that I'm right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你-你确-确-确定?\N{\rENG}A-a-are you s-sure? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能看到命运的轨迹一路延伸到时间的地平线\N{\rENG}I can see the path of fate as it stretches toward the horizon. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}红宝石躲避不了宿命\N{\rENG}Ruby can't avoid the inevitable. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她只是在让自己的情绪失控\N{\rENG}She's just letting her emotions get out of hand. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不是吗?\N{\rENG}N-n-not you, though? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.08,0:05:55.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...得去卫生间了\N{\rENG}I'm...Going to the bathroom. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}同样无法避免\N{\rENG}Also inevitable. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蓝宝石?\N{\rENG}Sapphire? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}马桶冻住了\N{\rENG}The toilet's frozen. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是命啊\N{\rENG}Such is fate. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那我也注定要去外面的草地上尿了?\N{\rENG}Am I fated to pee outside on the grass, too? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的\N{\rENG}Yes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拱顶石州...\N{\rENG}"Keystone state"...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 小子 我带晚餐了哦\N{\rENG}Hey, stu-ball, I brought dinner. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 老爸 怎么样?\N{\rENG}Hey, dad. How'd it go? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 他以前不是个凶手 这还不错\N{\rENG}Well, he wasn't an ex-murderer, so that was good. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.92,0:06:24.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你穿着浴衣在外面干什么?\N{\rENG}What are you doing outside in your bathing suit? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且石榴在哪?\N{\rENG}And where's Garnet? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他不会喜欢方形\N{\rENG}He's not going to like that it's square. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪 另一个呢?\N{\rENG}Oh, boy. Where's the other one? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在原来是泳池的地方散步呢\N{\rENG}She's pacing around in what used to be the pool. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有些非常严重的事情发生了\N{\rENG}Something pretty serious must be going on
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果都能让石榴分裂了的话\N{\rENG}if it made Garnet split up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但 嘿 我们仍能高兴起来啊\N{\rENG}But hey, we can still have a good time. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}方形的披萨?\N{\rENG}Square Pizza?! 
Dialogue: 600,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.38,Hint,,0,0,0,,第二季第2集说好的不介意任何基本形状呢?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个疯狂的州怎么了?\N{\rENG}What's wrong with this crazy state?! 
Dialogue: 600,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.66,Hint,,0,0,0,,"方形披萨"可能指的是宾夕法尼亚州东北部非常流行的"Old Forge style pizza"\N"Old Forge style pizza"通常使用American cheese\N而且通常叫"tray"( 盘) 和"cut"( 块) 而非"pie"( 张) 和"slice"( 片) 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}儿子 你生命中总有些时候\N{\rENG}Son, there'll come a time in your life
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得学会接受所有的披萨\N{\rENG}when you learn to accept all Pizza. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么红宝石和蓝宝石直接 和好呢?\N{\rENG}Why can't Ruby and Sapphire just make up? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有的时候相互爱恋的人\N{\rENG}Sometimes people that love each other
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可能会无意中相互伤害\N{\rENG}can hurt each other's feelings without meaning to. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们应该给他们点空间\N{\rENG}We should just give them some space. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我觉得她们能解决这个问题\N{\rENG}But I think they'd work it out
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果她们愿意沟通的话\N{\rENG}if they'd just talk to each other. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}明天早上一切都会变好的\N{\rENG}Everything will be better in the morning. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们都要去世界上最好的餐厅\N{\rENG}We'll all go to the best diner in the world, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们将吃到世界上最好的早餐\N{\rENG}where they'll eat the best breakfast in the world. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你觉得这有用吗?\N{\rENG}You think that'll help? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没什么能像早餐一样让人们团聚\N{\rENG}Nothing like a little breakfast to bring people together. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你确实是我最喜欢的老爸\N{\rENG}You really are my favorite dad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就知道这份披萨能帮到我\N{\rENG}I knew this Pizza would put me over the top. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.16,0:07:27.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿!\N{\rENG}Hey! 
Dialogue: 500,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.80,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\bord0\shad0\frx0\fry336\pos(528,530)\org(688,503.334)}{\fs64\c&HDEEC4D&}世界上\N{\fs128\c&H8232B8&}最好的{\fs64\c&HDEEC4D&}\N餐厅
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢!\N{\rENG}Thanks! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了? 不饿吗?\N{\rENG}What's the matter? Not hungry? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}宝石人不用吃饭 爸爸\N{\rENG}Gems don't need to eat, dad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 石榴有时会吃啊\N{\rENG}Eh, Garnet likes to eat sometimes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 显然 石榴 不 在!\N{\rENG}Ugh! Well, Garnet's not here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}唔 我的天!\N{\rENG}Mmm. Oh, boy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.08,0:07:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这-真的是-世界上-最好的餐厅!\N{\rENG}This really is the best diner in the world! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在晃桌子\N{\rENG}You're shaking the table. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢?! 哈!\N{\rENG}Oh?! Heh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 很好奇你居然还 有点感情 说实话!\N{\rENG}I'm kinda surprised you felt anything at all, to be honest! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-不需要-感觉 我能看到\N{\rENG}I didn't need to feel--I saw. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.88,0:08:10.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所 有 事你都 看 得 一清 二楚 不 是 吗?!\N{\rENG}Everything's just so crystal clear to you, isn't it?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.52,0:08:12.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这会过去了\N{\rENG}This will pass. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她迟早会让自己熄火的\N{\rENG}She'll eventually just burn herself out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是你 的 想 法!\N{\rENG}That's what you think! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是永不熄灭的烈焰 baby!\N{\rENG}I am an eternal flame, baby! 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.14,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}你又不了解我!\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}You don't know me! 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.06,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}我怎么可能不了解\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}How could I possibly not know you
Dialogue: 50,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.88,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}你看看你! 嗷～嚎-嚎\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}Look at you! Awww-haw-haw. 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.28,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}我们总是融合在一起\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}we always fused. 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.70,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}你都不了解你自己! 哈!\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&H5E37D3&}You don't even know yourself! Hah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 这没什么 伙计!\N{\rENG}Hey, it's okay, pal! 
Dialogue: 50,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.30,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}看看你自己 看看你在干什么...\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HE79069&}Look at you. Look at what you're going on about...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们仍然能解决的!\N{\rENG}We can still save this! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们为什么不讲这些打包带走然后-\N{\rENG}Why don't we just bag these up to go and--
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 天哪\N{\rENG}ah, geez. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当石榴说她要和我与爸爸\N{\rENG}I was so happy when Garnet said
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一起旅行时我还很高兴!\N{\rENG}she was gonna come on this trip with me and dad! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}家里糟透了 这里也糟透了!\N{\rENG}Home's been awful. Here's been awful! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为你们想放松一下\N{\rENG}I thought you wanted to have a fun time, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但每个人也都表现的非常糟糕!\N{\rENG}but everyone's been acting awful, too! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这种氛围-这种氛围一直跟着我们\N{\rENG}It--it just came with us. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就不理解了 是-这是因为我吗?\N{\rENG}I don't understand. Is it--is it me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不!\N{\rENG}No! Uh, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 都是我们的错!\N{\rENG}Steven, it's all us! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我们让他感觉这都是他的错\N{\rENG}But we made him feel like it was his fault. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.92,0:09:03.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我总是关注着未来\N{\rENG}I keep looking into the future
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那时这一切都已经被解决了\N{\rENG}when all of this has already been solved, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就好像你当下的感受毫无意义一样\N{\rENG}as if it doesn't matter how you feel in the present. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.70,0:09:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难怪-你觉得-我毫不-在乎!\N{\rENG}No wonder you think I don't care! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蓝宝石!\N{\rENG}Sapphire! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 不不不不!\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no, no! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这都是我的错!\N{\rENG}This is all my fault! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我并不想寻找解决方法\N{\rENG}I-I didn't want to look for a solution. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是在犯孩子气而已\N{\rENG}I just wanted to be mad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是对的 你一直是对的\N{\rENG}You're right. You're always right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前犯傻了\N{\rENG}I was being stupid. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不觉得你笨!\N{\rENG}I don't think you're stupid! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 对不起\N{\rENG}I'm, sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真的认为我对已经发生的毫不在意?\N{\rENG}You honestly think I'm not upset about what happened? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-只是试着做正确的事而已\N{\rENG}I was just trying to do the right thing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道\N{\rENG}I know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道分开的好处是什么吗?\N{\rENG}You know what's nice about being split up? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是什么?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能看到你了\N{\rENG}I get to look at you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.46,0:09:47.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噗!\N{\rENG}Pfft! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}严肃点!\N{\rENG}Be serious! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这才是我的爱笑的小蓝嘛!\N{\rENG}There's my laffy saffy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘! 你这是在史蒂文面前放闪光弹啊!\N{\rENG}Shh! You're embarrassing me in front of Steven! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 我为早餐付过钱了...\N{\rENG}Well, I paid for breakfast...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有桌子损坏的费用\N{\rENG}And the damage to the booth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不管怎么说 我觉得我放够假了\N{\rENG}Anyhoo, I think I'm all vacationed out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}准备好收拾东西了吗?\N{\rENG}Ready to call it a day? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}先得拿到免费冰块再说!\N{\rENG}Not before we get our free ice! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴!\N{\rENG}Garnet! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们到家～啦!\N{\rENG}We're home! 
Dialogue: 50,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.68,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_BKG}{\c&HB4C7E6&}我不知道为什么我总是-\N{\rENG_BKG}{\c&HB4C7E6&}I just don't know why I keep--
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 呃-你们看起来过得很开心啊\N{\rENG}Oh! Ah-you look like you all had fun. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊 问题解决了!\N{\rENG}Yeah, it all worked out! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴 你感觉怎么样?\N{\rENG}Garnet, how are you? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是现在\N{\rENG}Not now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她总算又和我说话了...算是\N{\rENG}She's speaking to me again...Kind of. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那真是一次超棒的旅行\N{\rENG}That really was a great trip. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能再去一次吗?\N{\rENG}Can we go back? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许吧...\N{\rENG}Maybe one day...But not to that diner. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但-不算那家餐馆\N{\rENG}But not to that diner. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.86,0:10:47.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 天哪\N{\rENG}Oh, boy. 
